---
import Button from "../shared/Button.astro";
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../shared/Paragraph.astro";
---

<section  id="cta" class="pb-20">
  <Container>
    <div
      class="w-full relative py-8 md:py-10 px-6 md:px-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-gray-100 to-gray-200 dark:from-gray-900"
    >
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-full flex justify-end">
        <div class="w-28 h-28 overflow-auto flex rounded-xl relative blur-2xl">
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -top-1 -right-1 bg-green-500 rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-[#FCDC58] rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -left-1 bg-primary rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
          </div>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 h-full w-full flex items-end">
        <div class="w-28 h-28 overflow-auto flex rounded-xl relative blur-2xl">
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -top-1 -right-1 bg-green-500 rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-[#FCDC58] rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -left-1 bg-primary rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto text-center max-w-xl md:max-w-2xl relative">
        <h1
          class="text-3xl/tight sm:text-4xl/tight md:text-5xl/tight
          font-bold text-heading-1"
        >
        Descubre ahora el <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 from-20% via-primary via-30% to-green-600">Futuro del Taxi</span> con Nuestro Servicio de Transporte.
        </h1>
        <Paragraph className={"pt-10"}>
          En el mundo actual, la tecnología y la comodidad son dos aspectos clave que los clientes buscan en sus servicios de transporte. Nuestro servicio de taxi está diseñado para ofrecerte una experiencia excepcional, combinando facilidad de uso, comodidad y eficiencia.
        </Paragraph>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-6">
            <a href=https://api.whatsapp.com/send/?phone=34666615100><img class="h-16 w-16 object-cover rounded-full" src="../../../public/images/whatsapp3.webp" alt="whasap"></a>
            <a href="tel:+34666615100"><img class="h-16 w-16 object-cover" src="../../../public/images/llamada3.webp" alt="telefono"></a>
            <a href="mailto:penarroyataxi@gmail.com?Subject=Solicitar%20presupuesto%20desplazamiento"><img class="h-16 w-16 object-cover" src="../../../public/images/correo3.webp" alt="correo"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
